[{"text": "I'm going to speak", "start": 12.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about a tiny, little idea.", "start": 14.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And this is about shifting baseline.", "start": 17.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And because the idea can be explained in one minute,", "start": 21.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "I will tell you three stories before", "start": 25.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to fill in the time.", "start": 28.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the first story", "start": 30.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is about Charles Darwin, one of my heroes.", "start": 32.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And he was here, as you well know, in '35.", "start": 35.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And you'd think he was chasing finches,", "start": 38.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but he wasn't.", "start": 40.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "He was actually collecting fish.", "start": 42.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And he described one of them", "start": 44.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as very \"common.\"", "start": 46.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This was the sailfin grouper.", "start": 48.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "A big fishery was run on it", "start": 50.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "until the '80s.", "start": 52.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now the fish is on the IUCN Red List.", "start": 55.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now this story,", "start": 58.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have heard it lots of times", "start": 60.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on Galapagos and other places,", "start": 63.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so there is nothing particular about it.", "start": 65.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But the point is, we still come to Galapagos.", "start": 68.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We still think it is pristine.", "start": 71.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The brochures still say", "start": 74.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it is untouched.", "start": 77.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So what happens here?", "start": 79.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The second story, also to illustrate another concept,", "start": 82.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is called shifting waistline.", "start": 85.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 87.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Because I was there in '71,", "start": 90.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "studying a lagoon in West Africa.", "start": 92.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was there because I grew up in Europe", "start": 94.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I wanted later to work in Africa.", "start": 97.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I thought I could blend in.", "start": 99.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I got a big sunburn,", "start": 101.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I was convinced that I was really not from there.", "start": 103.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This was my first sunburn.", "start": 106.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the lagoon", "start": 108.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "was surrounded by palm trees,", "start": 111.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as you can see, and a few mangrove.", "start": 113.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And it had tilapia", "start": 115.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about 20 centimeters,", "start": 117.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a species of tilapia called blackchin tilapia.", "start": 119.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the fisheries for this tilapia", "start": 121.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "sustained lots of fish and they had a good time", "start": 123.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and they earned more than average", "start": 126.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in Ghana.", "start": 128.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "When I went there 27 years later,", "start": 130.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the fish had shrunk to half of their size.", "start": 133.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They were maturing at five centimeters.", "start": 136.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They had been pushed genetically.", "start": 138.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "There were still fishes.", "start": 140.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They were still kind of happy.", "start": 142.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the fish also were happy to be there.", "start": 144.0, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "So nothing has changed,", "start": 149.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but everything has changed.", "start": 151.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My third little story", "start": 153.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that I was an accomplice", "start": 155.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the introduction of trawling", "start": 157.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in Southeast Asia.", "start": 159.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In the '70s -- well, beginning in the '60s --", "start": 161.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Europe did lots of development projects.", "start": 164.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Fish development", "start": 167.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "meant imposing on countries", "start": 169.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that had already 100,000 fishers", "start": 171.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to impose on them industrial fishing.", "start": 174.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And this boat, quite ugly,", "start": 177.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is called the Mutiara 4.", "start": 179.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I went sailing on it,", "start": 181.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we did surveys", "start": 183.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "throughout the southern South China sea", "start": 186.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and especially the Java Sea.", "start": 189.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And what we caught,", "start": 191.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we didn't have words for it.", "start": 193.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "What we caught, I know now,", "start": 195.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is the bottom of the sea.", "start": 198.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And 90 percent of our catch", "start": 200.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "were sponges,", "start": 202.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "other animals that are fixed on the bottom.", "start": 204.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And actually most of the fish,", "start": 207.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they are a little spot on the debris,", "start": 209.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the piles of debris, were coral reef fish.", "start": 211.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Essentially the bottom of the sea came onto the deck", "start": 214.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and then was thrown down.", "start": 216.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And these pictures are extraordinary", "start": 218.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because this transition is very rapid.", "start": 221.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Within a year, you do a survey", "start": 224.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and then commercial fishing begins.", "start": 227.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The bottom is transformed", "start": 229.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from, in this case, a hard bottom or soft coral", "start": 231.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "into a muddy mess.", "start": 234.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is a dead turtle.", "start": 237.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They were not eaten, they were thrown away because they were dead.", "start": 239.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And one time we caught a live one.", "start": 242.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It was not drowned yet.", "start": 244.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And then they wanted to kill it because it was good to eat.", "start": 246.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This mountain of debris", "start": 249.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is actually collected by fishers", "start": 252.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "every time they go", "start": 255.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "into an area that's never been fished.", "start": 257.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But it's not documented.", "start": 259.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We transform the world,", "start": 261.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but we don't remember it.", "start": 263.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We adjust our baseline", "start": 265.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to the new level,", "start": 268.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we don't recall what was there.", "start": 270.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "If you generalize this,", "start": 274.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "something like this happens.", "start": 276.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You have on the y axis some good thing:", "start": 278.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "biodiversity, numbers of orca,", "start": 281.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the greenness of your country, the water supply.", "start": 284.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And over time it changes --", "start": 287.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it changes", "start": 289.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because people do things, or naturally.", "start": 291.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Every generation", "start": 293.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "will use the images", "start": 295.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that they got at the beginning of their conscious lives", "start": 297.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as a standard", "start": 300.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and will extrapolate forward.", "start": 302.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the difference then,", "start": 304.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they perceive as a loss.", "start": 306.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But they don't perceive what happened before as a loss.", "start": 308.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You can have a succession of changes.", "start": 311.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "At the end you want to sustain", "start": 313.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "miserable leftovers.", "start": 316.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And that, to a large extent, is what we want to do now.", "start": 319.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We want to sustain things that are gone", "start": 322.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or things that are not the way they were.", "start": 325.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Now one should think", "start": 329.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this problem affected people", "start": 331.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "certainly when in predatory societies,", "start": 333.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "they killed animals", "start": 337.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and they didn't know they had done so", "start": 339.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "after a few generations.", "start": 341.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Because, obviously,", "start": 343.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "an animal that is very abundant,", "start": 346.0, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "before it gets extinct,", "start": 351.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it becomes rare.", "start": 354.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So you don't lose abundant animals.", "start": 357.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You always lose rare animals.", "start": 360.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And therefore they're not perceived", "start": 362.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as a big loss.", "start": 364.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Over time,", "start": 366.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we concentrate on large animals,", "start": 368.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and in a sea that means the big fish.", "start": 370.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They become rarer because we fish them.", "start": 372.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Over time we have a few fish left", "start": 375.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we think this is the baseline.", "start": 377.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And the question is,", "start": 380.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "why do people accept this?", "start": 382.0, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "Well because they don't know that it was different.", "start": 387.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And in fact, lots of people, scientists,", "start": 390.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "will contest that it was really different.", "start": 393.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And they will contest this", "start": 395.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because the evidence", "start": 397.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "presented in an earlier mode", "start": 399.0, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "is not in the way", "start": 404.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "they would like the evidence presented.", "start": 407.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "For example,", "start": 409.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the anecdote that some present,", "start": 411.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as Captain so-and-so", "start": 413.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "observed lots of fish in this area", "start": 415.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "cannot be used", "start": 418.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or is usually not utilized by fishery scientists,", "start": 420.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because it's not \"scientific.\"", "start": 423.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So you have a situation", "start": 425.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where people don't know the past,", "start": 427.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "even though we live in literate societies,", "start": 430.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because they don't trust", "start": 433.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the sources of the past.", "start": 435.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And hence, the enormous role", "start": 438.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that a marine protected area can play.", "start": 441.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Because with marine protected areas,", "start": 443.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we actually recreate the past.", "start": 446.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "We recreate the past that people cannot conceive", "start": 450.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because the baseline has shifted", "start": 453.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and is extremely low.", "start": 455.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "That is for people", "start": 457.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who can see a marine protected area", "start": 459.0, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "and who can benefit", "start": 464.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from the insight that it provides,", "start": 466.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which enables them to reset their baseline.", "start": 469.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "How about the people who can't do that", "start": 473.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because they have no access --", "start": 475.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the people in the Midwest for example?", "start": 477.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There I think", "start": 480.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the arts and film", "start": 482.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "can perhaps fill the gap,", "start": 484.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and simulation.", "start": 486.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is a simulation of Chesapeake Bay.", "start": 488.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There were gray whales in Chesapeake Bay a long time ago --", "start": 491.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "500 years ago.", "start": 493.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And you will have noticed that the hues and tones", "start": 495.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are like \"Avatar.\"", "start": 498.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 500.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And if you think about \"Avatar,\"", "start": 502.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if you think of why people were so touched by it --", "start": 504.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "never mind the Pocahontas story --", "start": 507.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "why so touched by the imagery?", "start": 511.0, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Because it evokes something", "start": 515.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that in a sense has been lost.", "start": 518.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And so my recommendation,", "start": 520.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it's the only one I will provide,", "start": 522.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is for Cameron to do \"Avatar II\" underwater.", "start": 524.0, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "Thank you very much.", "start": 529.0, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 531.0, "duration": 2.0}]